{"title":"Sensors Overview","text":"<p>\u539f\u6587\u5730\u5740: <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http:\/\/docs.eoeandroid.com\/guide\/topics\/sensors\/sensors_overview.html\">http:\/\/docs.eoeandroid.com\/guide\/topics\/sensors\/sensors_overview.html<\/a>  <br \/>\n\u7ffb\u8bd1\u8005: <a href=\"http:\/\/wiki.eoeandroid.com\/index.php?title=AlbertLi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AlbertLi\uff08\u5c1a\u672a\u64b0\u5199\uff09\">AlbertLi<\/a> <br \/>\n\u6700\u540e\u66f4\u65b0:2012-06-13 \n<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http:\/\/docs.eoeandroid.com\/guide\/topics\/sensors\/index.html\">sensor:<\/a><\/b>\n<\/p><p><br \/>\n<\/p>\n<table id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><tr><td><div id=\"toctitle\"><h2>\u76ee\u5f55<\/h2><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E6.A6.82.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1<\/span> <span class=\"toctext\">\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u6982\u8ff0<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E4.BB.8B.E7.BB.8D\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2<\/span> <span class=\"toctext\">\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u4ecb\u7ecd<\/span><\/a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E6.A1.86.E6.9E.B6\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1<\/span> <span class=\"toctext\">\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u6846\u67b6<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E5.8F.AF.E7.94.A8.E6.80.A7\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2<\/span> <span class=\"toctext\">\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u53ef\u7528\u6027<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E8.AF.86.E5.88.AB.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E5.92.8C.E6.84.9F.E5.BA.94.E5.99.A8.E5.8A.9F.E8.83.BD\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3<\/span> <span class=\"toctext\">\u8bc6\u522b\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u548c\u611f\u5e94\u5668\u529f\u80fd<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n